nodes.text: Cellheim Anujo was the humanoid aide to Senator Tundra Dowmeia during the latter stages of the Clone Wars.
A mysterious being, Cellheim Anujo was often draped in black robes and veils that masked both gender and species.
Cellheim Anujo was principally played by T.V. Moore on all the Australian main unit scenes and also by Dean Mitchell for the UK Unit pick up shots on Revenge of the Sith.
Cellheim Anujo was originally known only as "Tundra Dowmeia's aide".
